character.name:
Isometric pixel art monster, 64x64,
fantasy RPG style similar to Dofus 1.29,
a small goblin creature,
green skin, big pointed ears,
leather armor pieces,
simple dagger in hand,
slightly hunched posture,
mischievous and aggressive expression,
clear readable silhouette,
limited color palette,
clean pixel art shading,
game asset, transparent background
